oluten Zahl der Opfer entgegenstehen. Die hier anhand einer regional gegliederten Darlegung der gesicherten Erkenntnisse gezogene Bilanz ermittelt die Größenordnung des Völkermords jenseits aller Spekulationen.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a FA license: uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/free-access-policy uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aHolocaust, Jewish (1939-1945). 0aNational socialism. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aArndt, Ino, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBenz, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBenz, Wolfgang, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBoberach, Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFleischer, Hagen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGolczewski, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrimm, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHirsehfeld, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoppe, Hans-Joachim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMendelsohn, Oskar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoser, Jonny, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPicciotto Fargion, Liliana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRöbel, Gert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmidt-Hartmann, Eva, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSundhaussen, Holm, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVarga, László, econtributor.4